{
  "texts": [
    "Non-rigid registration is essential for human point cloud data, joints, deformation, etc.",
    "Compared with rigid registration, non-rigid point cloud registration needs to consider deformation in addition to the above challenges, which leads to larger solution space.",
    "This is also a big challenge for researchers.",
    "The current mainstream methods can be divided into two categories: displacement-based and flow-based models.",
    "However, only a few researches on non-rigid point cloud registration are based on deep learning."
  ]
}